dc_title_s: The Balkans 1:250,000. Kalamai, sheet G-13. A.M.S. M506 (G.S.G.S. 4410)
dc_description_s: AMS 2. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4410. Alternate title: Kalamai. Transverse Mercator projection. Principal meridians are Athens and Greenwich. Universal transverse Mercator and Mediterranean zone grids. UTM grid added and gradient tints and air information deleted by AMS 1948. Relief shown by 100 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. With a Greek glossary. Compiled by 512 Fd. Survey Coy., R. E., June, 1944. See index. Library holdings for this set are incomplete.
dc_publisher_s: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1948.
